import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { View, Dimensions, Pressable } from 'react-native';
import Svg, { Path, Rect, Defs, LinearGradient, Stop, Text, Filter, feDropShadow } from 'react-native-svg';

const OctahedronSvg = ({ style, ...props }) => {
  const [isPressed, setIsPressed] = useState(false);
  
  // Original SVG dimensions
  const originalWidth = 492;
  const originalHeight = 467;
  const aspectRatio = originalHeight / originalWidth;

  // Get screen width and calculate responsive height
  const screenWidth = Dimensions.get('window').width;
  const containerWidth = Math.min(screenWidth * 0.8, originalWidth); // 80% of screen width, max original size
  const containerHeight = containerWidth * aspectRatio;

  return (
    <Pressable 
      onPressIn={() => setIsPressed(true)}
      onPressOut={() => setIsPressed(false)}
      style={[
        {
          width: '100%',
          aspectRatio: originalWidth / originalHeight,
          justifyContent: 'center',
          alignItems: 'center',
          transform: [{ scale: isPressed ? 0.98 : 1 }],
        },
        style
      ]}
    >
      <Svg
        width="100%"
        height="100%"
        viewBox={`0 0 ${originalWidth} ${originalHeight}`}
        preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
        fill="none"
        {...props}
      >
        <Defs>
          {/* Add shadow filter */}
          <Filter id="shadow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
            <feDropShadow dx="0" dy="0" stdDeviation="3" floodColor="#F4E409" floodOpacity="0.5"/>
          </Filter>

          {/* Enhanced gradients for 3D effect */}
          <LinearGradient id="octahedronGradient1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
            <Stop offset="0%" stopColor="#2C1A0B"/>
            <Stop offset="50%" stopColor="#3C2A1B"/>
            <Stop offset="100%" stopColor="#2C1A0B"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="octahedronGradient2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
            <Stop offset="0%" stopColor="#A3930A"/>
            <Stop offset="50%" stopColor="#B3A31A"/>
            <Stop offset="100%" stopColor="#A3930A"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          {/* Original gradients remain but enhanced */}
          <LinearGradient id="paint0_linear" x1="247.5" y1="78" x2="247.5" y2="158.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="0.6" stopColor="#B3A31A"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
          </LinearGradient>
          
          <LinearGradient id="paint1_linear" x1="298.646" y1="177.537" x2="337.537" y2="138.646" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="0.555" stopColor="#5F5906"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint2_linear" x1="195.537" y1="178.245" x2="156.646" y2="139.354" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="0.555" stopColor="#5F5906"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint3_linear" x1="196.244" y1="289.354" x2="157.353" y2="328.244" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="0.555" stopColor="#5F5906"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint4_linear" x1="299.354" y1="288.646" x2="338.244" y2="327.537" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="0.555" stopColor="#5F5906"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint5_linear" x1="247.5" y1="389.5" x2="247.5" y2="309" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint6_linear" x1="96" y1="229.5" x2="176.5" y2="229.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
          </LinearGradient>

          <LinearGradient id="paint7_linear" x1="399.5" y1="238.5" x2="319" y2="238.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <Stop stopColor="#F4E409"/>
            <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#8E8505"/>
          </LinearGradient>
        </Defs>

        {/* Central Octahedron with enhanced gradients and shadow */}
        <Path 
          d="M197.91 231.032L223.165 243.006L244.986 285.922L197.91 231.032Z" 
          fill="url(#octahedronGradient1)" 
          stroke="#F4E409" 
          strokeWidth={1.5}
          filter="url(#shadow)"
        />
        <Path 
          d="M196.853 229.424L246.063 179.975L223.253 241.941L196.853 229.424Z" 
          fill="url(#octahedronGradient2)" 
          fillOpacity="0.95" 
          stroke="#F4E409" 
          strokeWidth={1.5}
          filter="url(#shadow)"
        />
        <Path 
          d="M224.323 243.077L297.36 238.425L247.456 288.573L224.323 243.077Z" 
          fill="url(#octahedronGradient2)" 
          fillOpacity="0.95" 
          stroke="#F4E409" 
          strokeWidth={1.5}
          filter="url(#shadow)"
        />
        <Path 
          d="M224.267 242.079L247.498 178.972L297.614 237.407L224.267 242.079Z" 
          fill="url(#octahedronGradient1)" 
          stroke="#F4E409" 
          strokeWidth={1.5}
          filter="url(#shadow)"
        />

        {/* Text elements with enhanced interaction */}
        <Text
          x="157"
          y="139"
          fill="#F4E409"
          fillOpacity={isPressed ? "0.25" : "0.15"}
          fontFamily="Orbitron"
          fontSize="24"
          textAnchor="end"
        >
          Personalised
        </Text>

        <Text
          x="337.891"
          y="139"
          fill="#F4E409"
          fillOpacity={isPressed ? "0.25" : "0.15"}
          fontFamily="Orbitron"
          fontSize="24"
          textAnchor="start"
        >
          Easy to use
        </Text>

        <Text
          x="157"
          y="327.891"
          fill="#F4E409"
          fillOpacity={isPressed ? "0.25" : "0.15"}
          fontFamily="Orbitron"
          fontSize="24"
          textAnchor="end"
        >
          Web 3 native
        </Text>

        <Text
          x="337.891"
          y="327.891"
          fill="#F4E409"
          fillOpacity={isPressed ? "0.25" : "0.15"}
          fontFamily="Orbitron"
          fontSize="24"
          textAnchor="start"
        >
          Secure
        </Text>

        {/* Dotted Lines - refined dash pattern and gradient */}
        <Path d="M247 158.5V78" stroke="url(#paint0_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        <Path d="M337.891 139L299 177.891" stroke="url(#paint1_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        <Path d="M157 139.001L195.891 177.892" stroke="url(#paint2_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        <Path d="M157 327.891L195.891 289" stroke="url(#paint3_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        <Path d="M337.891 327.891L299 289" stroke="url(#paint4_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        <Path d="M247 309V389.5" stroke="url(#paint5_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        <Path d="M176.5 230H96" stroke="url(#paint6_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
        <Path d="M319 238H399.5" stroke="url(#paint7_linear)" strokeWidth={1.5} strokeDasharray="8 12"/>
      </Svg>
    </Pressable>
  );
};

export default OctahedronSvg;
